subtitle: Arms Trafficking
content:
Purchase the McKenzie Field Hangar and complete a mission for Oscar to unlock Arms Trafficking and whizz around the map stealing aircraft, narcotics, and weapons for several buyers Oscar has lined up. Heâ€™ll give you all the tools you need including weaponized vehicles and plenty of intel.

Purchase the McKenzie Field Hangar from the Maze Bank Foreclosures website. The missions will then be available from the laptop in the office or from your phone.
